    <article class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="What is the Upload Illustrations feature?" class="article-title">
          What is the Upload Illustrations feature?
          
        </h1>

        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p>The Upload Illustrations feature is used to directly upload illustrations and images to posts of novel works.</p>
<p><br>Take a look below if you'd like to learn how to use this feature.</p>
<p>▶︎<a href="#h_01ET2FXSWNHK22A79D5AMG39P4" target="_self" rel="undefined">On desktop</a></p>
<p>▶︎<a href="#h_01ET2FY2PS4RH4WJYRM6ND0EPN" target="_self" rel="undefined">On mobile</a></p>
<h2 id="h_01ET2FXSWNHK22A79D5AMG39P4">On desktop</h2>
<p>Click the "Tool" drop-down menu on the novel posting page, then click "Upload illustrations".</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900005252926/ugaw0X_AryJ49ddZeaKDzneYf-phbjDobhLjPg-5mpzO04gTDm2mrpN4GNk1h1YPzffpRdnGpUzto6ekdUjsJU-LLoq2cgYHSQAn0XXxEqrvkQjsmQDiP2r3tMPrHoJJdhOP3a5k.png" alt="ugaw0X_AryJ49ddZeaKDzneYf-phbjDobhLjPg-5mpzO04gTDm2mrpN4GNk1h1YPzffpRdnGpUzto6ekdUjsJU-LLoq2cgYHSQAn0XXxEqrvkQjsmQDiP2r3tMPrHoJJdhOP3a5k.png"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Please upload your images via the menu that pops up. You can upload multiple images at a time.</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900006897503/mceclip0.png" alt="mceclip0.png"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>You can change the order of the images as well as delete them by clicking the "Edit" button.</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900005986706/mceclip1.png" alt="mceclip1.png"></p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900006897763/mceclip2.png" alt="mceclip2.png"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>When you've finished uploading the images, the uploaded image tags will be added to your work.</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900006177243/yllEsIACDdvn1_8HregnxvNe8CNSebGETjnU6edjsdvSNRTe01iHdfuu_I4weC6i9y0006i4JWSdlhcqJ5krsq3wm_-Fnz3Fqr5d8O8BUx9ZHK1JLzAqhuDbnb92gyv2maefdw3Y.jpg" alt="yllEsIACDdvn1_8HregnxvNe8CNSebGETjnU6edjsdvSNRTe01iHdfuu_I4weC6i9y0006i4JWSdlhcqJ5krsq3wm_-Fnz3Fqr5d8O8BUx9ZHK1JLzAqhuDbnb92gyv2maefdw3Y.jpg"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The location of the tag inside your work is where the illustrations will be displayed.</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900006177263/SNyCHAUbPEuIrHwWDMA-uW7C1vNoRB-y016LqRGDAbaoJSzL_1OOAtwaX4JGxvCRQd5PCFozdzvPLuA_xAywLGvBIRahBI24uw5oRczAZQgm0fHwe21U-ny8FHKJRCNhzcy_bMu7.jpg" alt="SNyCHAUbPEuIrHwWDMA-uW7C1vNoRB-y016LqRGDAbaoJSzL_1OOAtwaX4JGxvCRQd5PCFozdzvPLuA_xAywLGvBIRahBI24uw5oRczAZQgm0fHwe21U-ny8FHKJRCNhzcy_bMu7.jpg"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2 id="h_01ET2FY2PS4RH4WJYRM6ND0EPN">On mobile</h2>
<p>Click the "Tool" drop-down menu on the novel posting page, then click "Illustration (upload)".</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900006180063/KU2_W8yMJ7k48VTWXDvILx-RxA_ipkdEG0BS0OvVpDGeq-9zb0OdaOn2W6dQK2Ue1jfhNrbaIwik4bUTgjWLknCxMeHBS_uoJ2MTeDv_SNa2UmNM65Dd-gbHe5esl8uZuoopCinM.png" alt="KU2_W8yMJ7k48VTWXDvILx-RxA_ipkdEG0BS0OvVpDGeq-9zb0OdaOn2W6dQK2Ue1jfhNrbaIwik4bUTgjWLknCxMeHBS_uoJ2MTeDv_SNa2UmNM65Dd-gbHe5esl8uZuoopCinM.png"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Please upload your images via the menu that pops up. You can upload multiple images at a time.</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900006897963/mceclip5.png" alt="mceclip5.png"><br><br></p>
<p>You can change the order of the images as well as delete them by clicking the "Edit" button.</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900005986926/mceclip7.png" alt="mceclip7.png"></p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900006898063/mceclip8.png" alt="mceclip8.png"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>When you've finished uploading the images, the uploaded image tags will be added to your work.</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900005253026/1iM5Pd8gfQmilogZbNrPlmpj1D31lDFqIkfAfJ6IwY2BHjAYGLrWYlqFWwVfoUm-ZrKSfVQpdhdRbl4A4z5n0pCR8hbn08pCF23gKbt_AJrvpomY0fMc3-kzwj0l4-zta8gxA56b.jpg" alt="1iM5Pd8gfQmilogZbNrPlmpj1D31lDFqIkfAfJ6IwY2BHjAYGLrWYlqFWwVfoUm-ZrKSfVQpdhdRbl4A4z5n0pCR8hbn08pCF23gKbt_AJrvpomY0fMc3-kzwj0l4-zta8gxA56b.jpg"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The location of the tag inside your work is where the illustrations will be displayed.</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900006180083/XovCkqiRk640qaZ9kpDI1iIpOV-LTjb_GPXpUaVetloZ0NEFL1-_FJNLRUK7uOQ1AQzvLGwaEukywUiUwZZ6-cD7jwPl0MbmM2JAtOabp0nFP0G0nl89v0Y9JDzjJ2y2tItb7yP6.png" alt="XovCkqiRk640qaZ9kpDI1iIpOV-LTjb_GPXpUaVetloZ0NEFL1-_FJNLRUK7uOQ1AQzvLGwaEukywUiUwZZ6-cD7jwPl0MbmM2JAtOabp0nFP0G0nl89v0Y9JDzjJ2y2tItb7yP6.png"></p></div>

          <div class="article-attachments">
            <ul class="attachments">
              
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

